snippet.title: Stormgate Official Game Awards 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the all-new science fantasy universe of Stormgate, the upcoming real-time strategy game (RTS) from Frost Giant Studios, including former developers of StarCraft II and Warcraft III. 

Campaign. Co-op. Competitive. Custom Games. RTS is back.

Stormgate is in Closed Beta testing and will be released on Steam Early Access in Summer 2024. 
Become a Founder and join the future of RTS: https://playstormgate.com.

Premiered at the Game Awards on December 7, 2023.

#thegameawards #stormgate #rts #tga2023
